Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.44,JPO,,0,0,0,,アンジェロ？　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:36.52,JPO,,0,0,0,,ソイツが能力者を見つけてるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.98,JPO,,0,0,0,,サンキュー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.24,JPO,,0,0,118,,{\fn华文细黑\fs38\fscy106\fsp0\b0\blur0.5\bord0.8\shad1.2\4a80\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0F0F10&\4c&H393636&}Damn you…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.51,JPO,,0,0,0,,God, damn it! God!
